===Interpersonal love===
    −
Interpersonal love is love between two human beings, and is deeper than merely liking someone a lot. Although feelings are usually reciprocal, there can also be [[unrequited love]]. Interpersonal love is usually found in a [[interpersonal relationship]], such as between family members, friends, and couples. However, people often express love for other people outside of these relationships through charity and volunteering.

Interpersonal love is love between two human beings, and is deeper than merely liking someone a lot. Although feelings are usually reciprocal, there can also be [[unrequited love]]. Interpersonal love is usually found in an [[interpersonal relationship]], such as between family members, friends, and couples. However, people often express love for other people outside of these relationships through charity and volunteering.
